query: SELECT h.id, h.likes, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM highlight_likes hl WHERE hl.highlightId = h.id) as like_count FROM highlights h JOIN players p ON p.id = h.playerId WHERE p.fullName LIKE '%Hamza%';
